      <title>救援谈判陷入僵局，Northvolt 召开股东大会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/northvolt-calls-shareholder-meeting-as-rescue-talks-bog-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，电池制造商 Northvolt AB 于周三召开股东大会，筹集 3 亿美元紧急资金的谈判已进入关键时刻。]]></description>
